Wireshark Interface

The main window consists of three sections:

1. Packet List

Displays every captured packet.

Information includes:

Packet Number
Time
Source IP
Destination IP
Protocol
Packet Length
Summary
2. Packet Details

Shows detailed protocol information.

Example:

Ethernet
IPv4
TCP
HTTP
3. Packet Bytes

Displays the packet in hexadecimal and ASCII format.

