Advantages of Wireshark
Free and open source.
Supports thousands of protocols.
Excellent troubleshooting tool.
Useful for learning networking.
Used by network engineers and security analysts.
Limitations
Cannot decrypt encrypted HTTPS traffic without additional configuration.
Large captures can consume significant memory and storage.
Requires permission to capture packets.


